snippet.title: Super Jolly RPG - Release trailer
snippet.description:
It's Christmas eve, and our protagonist Shitstain wants to buy a present for his friend Flea. Alongside Ps, they explore the newly reopened forkville mall...

Will they be able to achieve their goals? Find out by playing the game:
https://agrimmora.itch.io/super-jolly-rpg

Dancing animation made by @GoldenDiossito
